data.description: Great potential for an investor or owner occupant with this West Toledo property.  This 3 bedroom, 1 bathroom home has a full basement for extra space and the kitchen has a cozy eat in nook. Lots of rental potential as is or great opportunity for improvements with a little sweat equity. Home features central A/C to keep cool in the summer, newer furnace (2019), and replacement windows. Come see what 1817 Fairfax can offer!
